Date of Birth: August 25, 1858<br/>
Birthplace: Salt Lake City, Utah, USA<br/>
Ordained apostle: October 7, 1897<br/>
Death: June 16, 1940<br/>
<br/>
Born Aug. 25, 1858, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, to Matthias Cowley and Sarah Elizabeth Foss.
Ordained apostle Oct. 7, 1897, by George Q. Cannon, at age 39; resigned Oct. 28, 1905; priesthood suspended May 11, 1911;
restored to full membership April 3, 1936; died June 16, 1940, at Salt Lake City, Salt Lake Co., Utah, at age 81.